Principal/ Licensed Real Estate Agent

As the Principal of Starr Partners Bankstown, Paul Nguyen adopts a personal and dedicated approach to helping buyers and vendors while utilising his wealth of experience gained working in the real estate industry to deliver great results for his customers. With an intimate knowledge of the Bankstown, South Western area and a very real enthusiasm for the property market, Paul is passionate about delivering exceptional results to every client he works with.

Being a long term resident of the Bankstown municipality, Paul has experienced the changing cultural and community aspects of the area, giving him an in-depth knowledge of the region�s many attributes and strengths. As a licensed Real Estate agent with over ten years experience in the home loans industry, he has supported many clients through the diverse challenges of buying and selling homes. Paul�s experience and knowledge, coupled with a sensitive and confidential approach, has built a strong level of customer loyalty for himself and Starr Partners Bankstown.

Paul's skills to negotiate and ability to advise between auction, private treaty or expressions of interest as the appropriate sale type has deliverd many superior outcomes with clients choosing Paul to handle the sale of their properties not only locally but further afield.

As both a leader and member of the sales team at Starr Partners Bankstown, Paul�s reputation, expertise and experience in handling customer relationships are of utmost important to him and result in the delivery of a value-packed, caring and professional service for all his clients.
